  "body": "### Description\r\nAs an implementor, I want to use hash_tree_root everywhere and get rid of merkle_root so that hashing logic is standardized and Artemis is compliant with the beacon chain spec. \r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* Miscellaneous type `HistoricalBatch` is defined as a list of `block_roots` and a list of `state_roots.` This will be serialized as an SSZ tuple, with both lists bounded by `SLOTS_PER_HISTORICAL_ROOT`.\r\n* Remove `merkle_root` function, and ensure all remaining instances of `merkle_root` in the transition logic now uses `hash_tree_root`.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\nSee https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/739\r\n",
